channel.title: RSPS Connection issues
channel.description: Hi, So lately I have been having trouble getting others to connect to my server. I was able to successfully port-forward and with the help of a friend, use no-ip. After compiling and sending over to said friend for testing purposes, I was able to connect fine, though he was unable to join the server. Additionally, the console kept spamming messages of debugging filter.executor or something like that the moment I joined. Any help? Thanks
